#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:670
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You don't know what they want, but do know you aren't interested in the "
"Theocracy's deals right now."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:672
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:676
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:685
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Another ship, seemingly foreign, arrives at the beacon shortly after you do,"
" looking uneasy. You could hail them and ask what's going on."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:688
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Hail them."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:690
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "\"Hello, military ship. Um... You don't look like a local\"."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:692
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Neither do you. What does it matter?."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:694
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The ship's captain hesitates a brief moment. \"You see, we are here on an... armament surveying mission you could say. And we need samples.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tYou make a mental note that this must be a secret mission, as the Ministry wouldn't normally be caught dead buying illegal weaponry."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:697
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Well why don't you go and get those samples?"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:699
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Maybe you look trustworthy enough to that captain, because he finally spills the beans. \n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"The people around here don't have the best reputation and it would be regrettable for us to be seen doing business with them. We were also not really provided the right equipment to take it by force from them and then leave this place in one piece...\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:702
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Ask them why they're telling you this."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:704
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "\"Well if you have any, would you sell us some?\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:708
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_BAM_FISSUREBEAM\"]/text"
msgstr "Sell them your Bada beam for 155~."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:710
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_BAM_FISSUREBEAM\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You try to hide your satisfaction while they transfer the excessive payment,"
" but also hope some unfortunate encounter won't make you regret the sale in "
"the near future. They leave without a word."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:719
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_RAIN_OF_ION\"]/text"
msgstr "Sell them your Rain of Ions shotgun for 180~."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:721
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_RAIN_OF_ION\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You try to hide your satisfaction while they transfer the excessive payment,"
" but also hope some unfortunate encounter won't make you regret the sale in "
"the near future. They leave without a word."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:730
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_RAIN_OF_FIRE\"]/text"
msgstr "Sell them your Rain of Fire launcher for 120~."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:732
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_RAIN_OF_FIRE\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You try to hide your satisfaction while they transfer the excessive payment,"
" but also hope some unfortunate encounter won't make you regret the sale in "
"the near future."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:741
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_LASER_BPS\"]/text"
msgstr "Sell them your BPS Messenger laser for 200~."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:743
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_LASER_BPS\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You try to hide your satisfaction while they transfer the excessive payment,"
" but also hope some unfortunate encounter won't make you regret the sale in "
"the near future."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:752
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[5]/text"
msgstr "Decline."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:754
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[5]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You think about the profit you could have made from this encounter, but also"
" remember that selling your weapons to random passerbys isn't a very safe "
"strategy."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:761
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"(RadiKal gear) Power up your weapons before they take YOUR equipment by "
"force."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:763
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Alright alright, no need to resort to violence, we'll be on our way now.\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:766
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"...Well that means they're as weak as they said, let's make some easy scrap!"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:768
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\"]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Wait... Wait! Thi-this was just a trade request. How did it come to this? Please!\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tAs you suspected from the covert nature of their mission, they're not sending any message to denounce you, merely firing up their engines to escape! Looks like you've found a place where crime can go unpunished..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:772
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:779
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Leave them be, they are clearly no threat."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:792
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Ignore them."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:794
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You leave them to whatever troubles they're having, and think about doing "
"some maintenance on your ship instead."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:796
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:800
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:818
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN_GOTAWAY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Zoltans escape before you can slaughter them for scrap, and contrary to "
"what you thought, actually do denounce you. Fair enough."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:820
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN_GOTAWAY\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:831
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You find a welcoming, lively senior hermit in a small space station chock-full of civilian and military supplies, apparently all for herself. \n"
"\t\t\"Hello foreigner, I know all about this sector, care to listen and have some tea?\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:834
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Stay for a while. This could be helpful."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:836
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Name's Bruntilda. As you've certainly noticed, this sector is occupied by "
"three main subfactions, and they all have their own personality!\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:838
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Politely interrupt and ask where those supplies came from."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:840
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Oh, aren't you curious! You see my dear, my sons work in this sector in "
"\"management\" and \"marketing\" positions. At one point they realized they "
"didn't have the time or patience to assess newcomers and teach them our "
"ways. So they came up with this gig for their sweet ol' mama, and they're "
"always making sure I am cared for.\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:842
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "I see. Nice to meet you."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:844
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Now that you can guess why nobody's pillaged the place yet, there are things"
" you could learn about. \"What else would you like to know, dear?\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:846
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Think of some questions."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:857
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "We don't have time to waste with some grandma's \"intel\"."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:859
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You say goodbye, gaining and losing nothing, which isn't that bad when you "
"think about it."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:862
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:866
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:879
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/text"
msgstr "Ask her..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:881
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "... about the subfaction names."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:883
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"What kind of names are those? RadiKal Bam? Punk? Scorch? Is it from a kid's show or something?\" you ask.\n"
"\t\t\t\"Not much to it really. Since so many people have been calling them radicals from the beginning of this little operation, my sons and their little friends simply embraced it. The subfactions just needed a little extra to tell themselves apart, and people don't really like talking too much around here. So they kept it short and to the point. Also I've heard something about variables? I'm the exception, chatting is so enjoyable!\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:887
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Ask her something else."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:891
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Leave."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:893
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "You grab your things."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:895
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Alright, we'll be on our way now. Thank you for the tea."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:903
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "... about the RK equipment design philosophy."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:905
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Maybe you're just a little slow in the head, so just in case, let me lay it out for you.\n"
"\t\t\tMembers of Bam believe in the blunt efficiency of large, impactful, stunning hits or events. Such as a good bonk to the dome, like i taught my children!\n"
"\t\t\tThe Punk prefer technological superiority, counter-intelligence and all that jazz. They tend to bring less firepower and more fancy gadgets to the table.\n"
"\t\t\tLastly the Scorch just want to watch things burn, and have ways to make sure they do. Some jealous foreigners like to spout nonsense about pacts with otherwordly creatures, especially among the Scorch. Isn't it sad, how low people will go?\n"
"\t\t\tI hope that clears it up for y'all youngsters!\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:912
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Ask her something else."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:916
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Leave."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:918
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "You grab your things."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:920
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Alright, we'll be on our way now. Thank you for the tea."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:928
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "... about the prices."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:930
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"It takes a lot of specialized equipment to discreetly get so many crafting"
" materials into a hidden sector, or so my sons told me. That leads to high "
"prices, but not so much for the local production of course!\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:933
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Ask her something else."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:937
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Leave."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:939
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "You grab your things."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:941
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Alright, we'll be on our way now. Thank you for the tea."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:949
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "... about the contests."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:951
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"The inevitable but usually friendly rivalry between the factions leads to many confrontations to figure out whose equipment is the best. \n"
"\t\t\t\tEven tourists like you can partake, so long as they own a piece. Sometimes they even survive!\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:955
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[4]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Ask her something else."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:959
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[4]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Leave."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:961
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[4]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "You grab your things."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:963
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[4]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Alright, we'll be on our way now. Thank you for the tea."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:972
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[5]/text"
msgstr "Threaten her for the supplies!"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:974
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[5]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Emboldened by her physical frailty, you decide chatting is never gonna be as"
" useful as just taking what you want."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:976
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[5]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "How about you just shut up and give us all of those suppl-"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:978
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[5]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Before you can finish your despicable threat, you feel the cold dagger belonging to a cloaked security drone pressing on your neck, and realize this whole place is obviously heavily defended.\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\"Uneducated scallywags, eh? Another disappointment, but it is clear that our little business is attractive to this type of people. What a waste of good tea. Out with you now.\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:982
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[5]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Wait a sec! You won't believe it but, this really isn't who we are..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:984
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[5]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You shamefully \"offer\" some supplies as an apology, find out why the pile is so big, and tell your crew in very clear terms that this event is not to be talked about ever again.\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tYou also feel like even though this happened in this hidden sector, word of your lack of morals could somehow reach the outside world."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1002
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[6]/text"
msgstr "Alright, we'll be on our way now. Thank you for the tea."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1007
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_GOODBYE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"She looks cheerful. \"Why, thank you! Very few of you young'uns take a pause to listen to an old lady around these parts. For some reason they seem to favor... 'enhanced interrogation' I think the kids call it? Something about manufacturing details. Anyhoo, farewell!\"\n"
"\tYou notice a shuttle sent to share a little of her supplies with you. That job might be lonelier than it looks, and you wonder how often her sons visit her."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1013
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_GOODBYE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1026
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"As soon as you get here, you notice that you're surrounded by a small Zoltan fleet intercepting every ship passing through here. An urgent hail from a heavily armed Zoltan Elite comes through. \n"
"\tNeedless to say, it would look suspicious not to take the hail.\n"
"\t[Dev note: Adding fleet background crashes MV so, just imagine it.]"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1034
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Answer it."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1036
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"As you may know if you're not a brainless savage, this sector has been providing armament to the Duskbringers. We have recently started tackling this problem.\n"
"\t\t\tLike any vessel in transit in a lawless armament-manufacturing area like this one, you will be subjected to the mandatory thorough search for said armament. The fight against illegal weapon proliferation starts with you. Do not resist.\"\n"
"\t\t\tZoltans consider this area a very serious issue. If they find any RadiKal equipment, it may be confiscated, or you might be fined based on how many you're carrying."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1041
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Agree to the search."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1046
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Ask what happens if you refuse."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1048
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Thanks to the merciful recent amendment 3473-B delta, captains may choose to participate in the funding of control vessels like this one, and report to the closest Zoltan police station within 12 jump cycles instead of immediately submitting to the search.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tEven though you have no intention of taking that detour, they would leave you alone for now."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1053
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Pay up."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1055
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You begrudgingly transfer the scrap but manage to fake a smile, taking "
"comfort in the fact that your equipment's safe... at least for now."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1063
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Agree to the search."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1072
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Try to ignore it and just pass through."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1074
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"You admission of guilt in facilitating terrorist operations has been recorded and filed for the trial of any surviving spouse(s) and/or heir(s). You will not escape the law.\"\n"
"\t\t\tSounds like you'll have to fight your way through. In fact you wonder how you managed to convince yourself this could end any differently."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1079
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1087
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[@req=\"zoltan_peacekeeper\"]/text"
msgstr "(Zoltan Peacekeeper) Send the secret 'All clear' signal."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1089
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[@req=\"zoltan_peacekeeper\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Zoltan ship immediately stops and then finds someone else to harass."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1092
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[@req=\"zoltan_peacekeeper\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1096
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[@req=\"zoltan_peacekeeper\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1117
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_ACCEPT\"]/text"
msgstr "They come aboard and search your ship..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1120
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_ACCEPT\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1122
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_ACCEPT\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Luckily you had nothing to worry about, and after leaving your ship, without"
" a word the Zoltans immediately cut comms to focus on a different ship. You "
"wonder what could have happened. In any case this took a while, too long to "
"do anything special on your ship."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1124
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_ACCEPT\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1131
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_ACCEPT\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1133
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_ACCEPT\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Before long, they do find something. \"Understand that without justification"
" for this, which you may still provide, we will apply the necessary "
"sanctions, which may be a fine or outright confiscation of the offending "
"equipment. Both may be avoided if you willingly leave someone with us for "
"interrogation.\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1135
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_ACCEPT\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1151
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL[5]/event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Maybe you forgot you were carrying RadiKal gear, or maybe you just didn't "
"find a way to avoid the search. Regardless, they are now fining you for each"
" piece!"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1153
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL[5]/event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_SUM_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "Let them calculate your total fine."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1155
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL[5]/event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_SUM_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"One illegal piece of gear, take this minimal fine as a warning. If you had"
" any more \"RadiKal\" gear than that, we would have been forced to direct "
"you to the local Police Station for processing.\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1163
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL[5]/event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_SUM_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"2\"]/text"
msgstr "Let them calculate your total fine."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1165
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL[5]/event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_SUM_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"2\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Two illegal pieces of gear. You should really know better than to give up ethics for power.\"\n"
"\t\t\tSupposedly you can get some of your scrap back by surrendering your illegal gear at the Police Station, but somehow you doubt that. It might be worth it to pay them a visit regardless."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1175
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL[5]/event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_SUM_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"3\"]/text"
msgstr "Let them calculate your total fine."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1177
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL[5]/event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_SUM_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"3\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Three illegal pieces of gear... The federation really hires any random scum these days. We will be notifying your leadership.\"\n"
"\t\t\tSupposedly you can get some of your scrap back by surrendering your illegal gear at the Police Station, but somehow you doubt that. It might be worth it to pay them a visit regardless."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1188
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL[5]/event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_SUM_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"4\"]/text"
msgstr "Let them calculate your total fine."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1190
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL[5]/event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_SUM_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"4\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"FOUR or more illegal pieces of gear! What th-... I do not even wish to know. What a horrible person you must be. Luckily for you, this is the maximum fine stipulated in the applicable regulation. I suppose nobody foresaw that anyone would make themselves any more of a wretched menace to society than that.\"\n"
"\t\t\tSupposedly you can get some of your scrap back by surrendering your illegal gear at the Police Station, but somehow you doubt that. It might be worth it to pay them a visit regardless."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1201
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL[5]/event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[5]/text"
msgstr "Give someone up for interrogation instead."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1213
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL[5]/event[@name=\"RK_SEIZE_ONE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Our current mission order is to confiscate any criminal weaponry of mass "
"destruction called...\""

