"re-open comms with you. \"Thank you for not interfering my good sir. Imagine"
" how much easier business would be if we had more cowa- i mean nice "
"bystanders like you around? Here's some fuel for your exemplary behavior, "
"and we're off to celebrate!\" You scoop up the reward and briefly wonder "
"what could have put them in such a good mood."

