#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:2949
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"EXIT_RADIKAL_MAIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"I'll make it simple for you, we have a reputation to uphold. If you're not able to beat one of our gatekeepers, we can't let you leave and make RadiKal gear look bad with your incompetence.\n"
"\tThink about it. Why do you think folks fund all of this? That's because you've never heard of subpar RadiKal equipment, and this is one way to do quality control.\n"
"\tYou do get to pick your opponent, so choose wisely... yeah, that IS part of the skill test.\n"
"\tOh and, don't worry about killing crew in these ships, they're all purpose-grown illegal clones. In fact we'd like to see you try to kill them cleanly.\""

